   <li><a href="#TruMakGro">1.4 Truth-Making as Grounding</a></li>
   </ul></li>
<li><a href="#WhiRanTruEliMadTruIfAny">2. Which range of truths are eligible to be made true (if any are)?</a>
   <ul>
   <li><a href="#Max">2.1 Maximalism</a></li>
   <li><a href="#TruMakForNegTru">2.2 Truth-makers for Negative Truths</a></li>
   <li><a href="#TruForGenTru">2.3 Truthmakers for General Truths</a></li>
   <li><a href="#Opt">2.4 Optimalism</a></li>
   <li><a href="#TruSupUpoBei">2.5 Truth Supervenes Upon Being</a></li>
   </ul></li>
