   <ul>
   <li><a href="#CatChe">3.1 To catch a cheater</a></li>
   <li><a href="#TruDepBei">3.2 Truth Depends on Being</a></li>
   <li><a href="#TruCorDef">3.3 Truth: Correspondence and Deflationism</a></li>
   </ul></li>
<li><a href="#Bib">Bibliography</a></li>
