Macbride gave in Cambridge, Michaelmas 2012. For subsequent revisions
he is grateful to Helen Beebee, John Bigelow, Jeremy Butterfield, Ross
Cameron, Julian Dodd, Dominic Gregory, Ghislain Guigon, Jane Heal,
